Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:20:03.93,Flying_object,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\bord0\c&H000000&\frz20.893\fs43\pos(699,280)}Zbohom
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ona...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepatrí sa vojsť do niekoho izby bez dovolenia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.09,0:20:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechcela som.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.60,0:20:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemohla som... odolať.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.14,0:21:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poď sem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.46,0:21:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naozaj je obloha takáto?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie. Je oveľa krajšia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Je oveľa väčšia a nádhernejšia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.62,0:21:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nádherná.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.67,0:21:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raz ti ju ukážem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.13,0:21:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skutočnú oblohu.
